high_descs: turn around and move to the kitchen sink
grab a cup out of the sink
turn around and move over to the microwave
place the cup inside of the microwave, microwave it, and then take it back out
move to the coffee maker on the kitchen counter to the right
place the cup under the spout of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: place a microwave cup under the spout of the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Take the mug from in the sink.
Turn around and go to the black counter with the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Turn around and go to your left to the table with the coffee maker.
Put the mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug in the coffee maker.

high_descs: You will turn right and cross the room to reach the kitchen counter.
You grab an coffee mug from out of the sink and right.
You turn right, after crossing the room with the coffee mug.
You will open the microwave door and in closing the mug it you will turn the dial to start position green.
After the microwave is finished you pick up the mug and move to the other table to the right.
You will place the mug in the coffee maker machine.
anns.task_desc: the goal is to microwave an mug and distill the remains in an coffee maker.
